import { ExpandMore, Favorite, MoreVert, Share } from '@mui/icons-material'
import { Avatar, Card, CardActions, CardContent, CardHeader, CardMedia, Collapse, IconButton, List, ListItem, ListItemText, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const FeedsCard = ({ val }) => {
    return (
        <Card sx={{ Width: 500, marginTop: "2rem", boxShadow: "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35) 0px 5px 15px" }}>
            <CardHeader
                avatar={
                    <Avatar >
                        {val.by.charAt(0)}
                    </Avatar>
                }
                action={
                    <IconButton aria-label="settings">
                        <MoreVert />
                    </IconButton>
                }
                title={val.by}
            />
            <CardMedia component="img" height="20%" image={val.postIMG} alt={val.postTitle} />
            <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="h6" color="text.primary">
                    {val.by}: {val.postTitle}

                </Typography>
            </CardContent>
            <CardActions disableSpacing>
                <IconButton aria-label="add to favorites">
                    <Favorite />
                </IconButton>
                <IconButton aria-label="share">
                    <Share />
                </IconButton>
                <ExpandMore
                    aria-label="show more"
                >
                    <ExpandMore />
                </ExpandMore>
            </CardActions>
            <Collapse timeout="auto" unmountOnExit>
                <CardContent>
                    <List>
                        <ListItemText primary="Profile" />
                        {val.comments.map((val1) => {
                            return <>
                                <ListItemText primary={`${Object.keys(val1)[0]} : ${Object.values(val1)[0]} `} />
                            </>
                        })}
                        {/* {console.log(val.comments)} */}
                    </List>
                </CardContent>
            </Collapse>
        </Card>
    )
}

export default FeedsCard
